PN,35301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman with incurable breast cancer to
OL,4,Cwalk the Great Wall of China for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FA woman from the Scottish Borders will
OL,8,Fwalk the Great Wall of China to raise
OL,9,Fmoney for a breast cancer charity and
OL,10,Fpromote awareness of early detection.
OL,12,FAileen Mackay from Westruther will
OL,13,Ftackle the trek in aid of breast
OL,14,Fcancer awareness charity 'CoppaFeel',
OL,15,Faiming to raise #4,000.
OL,17,FAileen was first diagnosed with breast
OL,18,Fcancer in 2011, and was later
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with secondary metastatic
OL,20,Fbreast cancer in 2022.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman with incurable breast cancer to
OL,4,Cwalk the Great Wall of China for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FAileen has previously taken on
OL,8,Fchallenges such as hiking up Mount
OL,9,FKilimanjaro and Everest Base Camp.
OL,11,F120 people are taking part in this
OL,12,Flatest challenge, and participants aim
OL,13,Fto walk 50 to 100km of the Great Wall
OL,14,Fover five days in September.
OL,16,FAileen told ITV Border: "The Great
OL,17,FWall of China has always been on that
OL,18,Fwhat some people call a bucket list -
OL,19,Ffor me it's a living list - so I'm
OL,20,Freally excited about going to do that.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman with incurable breast cancer to
OL,4,Cwalk the Great Wall of China for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"It's one of those things that's a
OL,8,Fonce in a lifetime opportunity."
OL,10,FCoppaFeel urges people to be aware of
OL,11,Ftheir bodies so they can notice any
OL,12,Fchanges, to help detect breast cancers
OL,13,Fearly.
OL,15,FAileen first discovered a lump in her
OL,16,Fbreast in 2009, and received a breast
OL,17,Fcancer diagnosis two years later.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman with incurable breast cancer to
OL,4,Cwalk the Great Wall of China for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FAfter gruelling treatments she was
OL,8,Fgiven the 'all clear', until ten years
OL,9,Flater she began to experience "strange
OL,10,Fsensations" down the right side of her
OL,11,Fbody.
OL,13,FShe said: "I couldn't work my hand
OL,14,Fproperly... Not quite sure what that
OL,15,Fwas, I went to my GP and was
OL,16,Fimmediately sent to the hospital.
OL,18,F"Later on that day was told I had a
OL,19,Fbrain tumour, and we also found a lung
OL,20,Ftumour.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman with incurable breast cancer to
OL,4,Cwalk the Great Wall of China for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"It took a while to get a diagnosis,
OL,8,Fbut it was metastatic breast cancer.
OL,10,F"I had a craniotomy and a lung
OL,11,Fresection. And since then, I've just
OL,12,Fbeen living with incurable breast
OL,13,Fcancer."
OL,15,FAileen has refused to let her cancer
OL,16,Fhold her back, and takes daily walks
OL,17,Fto prepare for her Great Wall
OL,18,Fchallenge.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman with incurable breast cancer to
OL,4,Cwalk the Great Wall of China for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FShe says she wants to raise awareness
OL,8,Fof breast cancer in addition to
OL,9,Fsupporting the charity with cash.
OL,11,FAileen said: "I was quite young when I
OL,12,Fhad my cancer, had no risk factors.
OL,14,F"I just want to raise awareness that
OL,15,Fwe should be checking our chests
OL,16,Fregularly from a young age, whether
OL,17,Fwe're male or female.
OL,19,F"If you find something that is
OL,20,Fabnormal - go and get it checked out."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
